{
  "id": "S2P05K21",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "ASSIGNING VALUES TO KEYS",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Key assignments values may be assigned different types of"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "functions:  SPF primary commands, line commands, data"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "characters and strings, REXX edit macros, and keyboard macros."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For example, if we wanted to assign the Ctrl-B key to be"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the \"BROWSE\" primary command, we would make the following change."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "NAME             VALUE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl A+          x'01'"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl B+          BROWSE"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Ctrl C+          x'03'"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Hitting ENTER to make the change take effect, any subsequent"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "use of the Ctrl-B key would be as if the BROWSE command had"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "been entered on the primary command line."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
